start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Created a file, read a file</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Created a file, read a file</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Here's your complete DevOps project — <strong>CloudTask Manager</strong> 🚀</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">🏗️ Project: CloudTask Manager</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">A full-stack <strong>Task Management SaaS</strong> — perfect to showcase all your skills together.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">📦 What's in the project</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Frontend (React.js)</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">User login/signup with JWT</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Task dashboard: create, assign, update, delete tasks</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Axios calls to Node.js backend API</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Backend (Node.js + Express)</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">REST API with JWT authentication middleware</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">PostgreSQL via AWS RDS</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Dockerized and deployed to EC2</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">☁️ AWS Services Used</h4>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Service</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Purpose</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">EC2</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Runs Docker containers</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">RDS</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">PostgreSQL database</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">S3</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Static files &amp; logs</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">ECR</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Docker image registry</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">VPC + IAM</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Security &amp; networking</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">ALB</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Load balancer</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">CloudWatch</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Monitoring + alarms</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">🔁 DevOps Flow</h4>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Terraform</strong> provisions ALL AWS resources as code</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Docker</strong> containerizes both React &amp; Node apps</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>GitHub Actions</strong> CI/CD: push to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">main</code> → test → build → push ECR → deploy EC2</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>CloudWatch</strong> monitors CPU, errors, sends SNS email alerts</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">📁 GitHub Repo Structure</h4>
