</span></span><span>
</span><span>CloudTask Manager                              GitHub: github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/cloudtask-manager
</span><span>Full-Stack DevOps Project | React.js · Node.js · AWS · Docker · Terraform
</span><span>
</span><span>- Built a full-stack Task Management SaaS with React.js frontend and Node.js/Express REST API
</span><span>  with JWT authentication and PostgreSQL database
</span><span>
</span><span>- Containerized both services using Docker and Docker Compose for consistent
</span><span>  local and production environments
</span><span>
</span><span>- Provisioned complete AWS infrastructure using Terraform (IaC) including
</span><span>  EC2, RDS PostgreSQL, ECR, VPC, IAM roles, and Application Load Balancer
</span><span>
</span><span>- Built automated CI/CD pipeline using GitHub Actions:
</span><span>  code push → test → Docker build → push to AWS ECR → deploy to EC2
</span><span>
</span><span>- Configured AWS CloudWatch monitoring with CPU alarms, dashboards,
</span><span>  and SNS email alerts for production health tracking</span></code></pre></div></div>
