<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">🛑 Common Errors &amp; Fix</h3>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Error</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Fix</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">docker-compose not recognized</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Use <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">docker compose up --build</code> (no hyphen)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">port 3000 already in use</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Run <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">docker-compose down</code> then <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">docker-compose up --build</code></td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Cannot connect to Docker daemon</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Open Docker Desktop app and wait for it to start</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Error: pull access denied</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Run <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">docker-compose up --build</code> not just <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">up</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
