<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Login Page</strong> — shows the dark-themed login/register screen</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Dashboard</strong> — shows the Kanban board with To Do / In Progress / Done columns</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Architecture Diagram</strong> — shows the full AWS setup (ALB → EC2 → RDS, ECR, CloudWatch)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>CI/CD Pipeline</strong> — shows the full GitHub Actions flow from push to live deployment</li>
</ol>
